### Part 4: Dependencies Data Model & Store (3-4 hours)

**Goal:** Add dependency support to type system and store

**Files to Modify:**
1. `src/types/index.ts` - Add TaskDependency interface
2. `src/stores/useKanbanStore.ts` - Add dependency actions

**New Actions:**
- `addDependency(sourceTaskId, targetTaskId)` - Mark A blocks B
- `removeDependency(dependencyId)` - Remove dependency
- `getDependencies(taskId)` - Get all dependencies for a task
- `getBlockers(taskId)` - Get tasks blocking this task
